characteristics.desc: Ruler Sun so creation, life giving, intellectual, leaders, authoritative, genius, brilliance, egoistic,impulsiveness, self-centered, analytical, initiator. King like, authoritative, pioneers, royal, trend setters, leadership, ego, creative, stubborn, selfish. Donâ€™t fear thinking big, make big plans and investments.

Ruler Moon so peace, emotional, feminine in nature, inquisitive, intuitive and research oriented. Diplomacy, secrecy, deceit, intelligence, uniqueness and inner wisdom. Can bring revolutionary ideas and find peace if they can balance their passion with their purpose. Think from heart and not head. Emotional dis-balance. Gentle, slow, sensitive, attractive, intuitive, mood swing.

Hardworking, full of zeal, sincere and honest. Artistic, creative, happy- go-lucky attitude & strong desire for peace. Honor, respect & self esteem is their biggest possession. Confident, brilliant, romantic and luckiest of all numbers. Imaginative, healer, preacher, spiritual, relegious, counsellor, wise.

Ruler Uranus or Rahu so orderly shows hard work, practical, argumentative and determined. They are logical and scientific. Disciplined, organized, short-tempered, rebellious, abusive, stubborn, logical, impulsive, energetic, serious, down to earth, faithful, honest and Determined. Devoted partner but sometimes does not understand the emotions of others. They are great reformers but struggle hard to earn a living. They are revolutionaries and shrewd and can be successful in business and politics.

Ruler Mercury so energy, versatility, co-operation, intuitive. They love freedom & change. They know how to balance yourself. Enthusiastic and eager for acquiring knowledge. They come up with such ideas which are ahead of generations. They have calculative mind, fun loving, curious, versatile, flexible and accommodating. Either will keep working or will get work done from others. Happy go lucky, lazy, dark horse, entertaining, communicative.

Love, affection, peace, harmony, strong memory, artistic, romantic, communicator, manipulative, diplomatic, family-oriented, shrewd. The failure, struggles and delays force them to turn the obstacles around. They are entertainers, artists, creators and enjoy beauty. Represents accumulation of wealth for an accomplished life.

They are researchers, introvert, philosophical, emotional, relegious, occult, spiritual, low in confidence, inquisitive, very good healer. Inclined for mystic sciences, meditation & perfection. They are restless and have reserved and conservative nature. They earn by hard work and perseverance. Great observers and have very good imagination ability.

Ruler Saturn and they have great mental strength, result oriented and ambitious. Born leaders and possess executive or organizational skills. They will face problems in life like financial or loss of 1 parent or health. The come out of it easily. Though they are systematic but delay, laziness and lethargies is their biggest enemy. Struggle, laborious, hardwork, logical, argumentative, stubborn, law, finance.

Ruler Mars so selfless, forgiveness, charitable and generous. They are fighters and have to face, lot of struggles. They are adventurous, aggressive & courageous. They are quarrelsome & have a fiery nature. They have to face lot of struggles and delaysin life. If they do something that benefits the social cause then they get rewarded. Thinkers, planners, mentally strong, Unpredictable behaviour, warrior, rough n tough, good humanitarian, egoistic.
